{"tid":1031831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警隊「一姐」將出任申訴專員 林鄭稱有信心趙慧賢獨立公正","createTime":"2019-02-22T02:27:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T04:49:48.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"44ba06fd7a1ba65e5814c3832701d87a0526cdc8","tid":1031831,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T02:27:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h1roeDB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh1roeDB.png&h=991d3c49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特區政府今早公佈委任警隊首名女副處長趙慧賢為新任申訴專員，任期4月1日起生效，為期5年，接替任期屆滿決定退休的劉燕卿。<br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥根據《申訴專員條例》（第397章）作出委任，政府新聞公報指趙慧賢在警隊工作超過35年，負責調查、執行、政策制定和人事管理方面，形容她「經驗豐富，也具備卓越的領導才能及溝通技巧」。<br />\n<br />\n有「警隊前一姐」之稱的趙慧賢是本港首位出任警務處副處長的女性，政府形容趙備受政府內外人士尊重、獲得社會各界認同、她於警隊工作多年間成就斐然。林鄭指，有信心趙將是一位獨立和公正的申訴專員、以及帶領公署在提升公共行政更進一步。<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n林鄭又祝願任期即將屆滿的劉燕卿在未來的日子順心滿意。<br />\n<br />\n10萬蚊 100人分！<br />\n星期一至五晚上10點半<br />\n《動腦Q》Let's Q the money！<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2QW8LcI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2QW8LcI&d=YG7PnvT15JjBub1A77CHD06%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=4e557f0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2QW8LcI</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190222/59288929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190222%2F59288929&d=YG7PnvT15JjBub1A77CHD06%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=7ddcf2d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190222%2F59288929&h=7ccd5a07\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190222/59288929</a>"},{"pid":"8944f7481b7acb2ab8f51cfd005ab8a5c90e4a40","tid":1031831,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T02:28:18.000Z","msg":"搞到人無得做真一姐"},{"pid":"0bf05a5c65c01f6e973cb7355b26a8e732fe60e6","tid":1031831,"uid":771